data.description: IMMACULATE, BEAUTIFUL AND BARELY LIVED IN HOME NESTLED ON A QUIET STREET that attends ALEDO ISD.  From the moment you walk in you will adore  the EXTENDED WOOD LOOK TILE FLOORS.  The kitchen is an absolute Chef's Dream with an ABUNDANT of Countertop Space as well as Cabinetry and is very open to the family room. The Breakfast Nook is OVERSIZED , and makes entertaining easy and enjoyable. The Master Suite is Dream with a wall of windows overlooking the OVERSIZED BACKYARD. All secondary bedrooms and closets are nice in size.  MORNINGSTAR offers wonderful amenities and activities for everyone, and offers easy access to the highway, and nearby shopping and restaurants.
